3338dd1b-422f-4d1c-bfe8-6037de4cfedd.title: Phillipa
3338dd1b-422f-4d1c-bfe8-6037de4cfedd.text:
Hi, I'm Phillipa! Juliet's cousin? I like to keep an eye on
her, make sure that dashing young Romeo doesn't just
steal away from here under our plain old noses!

b3842c8d-7040-4928-b226-a7ccb240daab.title: Phillipa
b3842c8d-7040-4928-b226-a7ccb240daab.text:
He'd do it you know... he's ever so dashing, and
cavalier, in a wet blanket sort of way.

f4cbedc9-a9dc-43d3-b82f-f2c3e684ceae.title: Phillipa
f4cbedc9-a9dc-43d3-b82f-f2c3e684ceae.text:
Oh, hello... Juliet has told me what you're doing for her
and Romeo and I have to say, I'm very grateful to
you. Juliet deserves a bit of happiness in her life.

36087eee-37ad-4c66-9fd6-51047caf76b2.title: Phillipa
36087eee-37ad-4c66-9fd6-51047caf76b2.text:
And I'm sure Romeo is just the sort of jester to make
her laugh out loud... hysterically you might say. He
always brings a tear to my eyes... tears of happiness at
his foolish antics!

604a6aa0-2983-41ee-8801-7f2724c2ed6b.title: <player>
604a6aa0-2983-41ee-8801-7f2724c2ed6b.text: Oh, thanks... I like to do my cupid bit.

67f09bcf-5201-4fbe-93ea-085bea462084.title: Phillipa
67f09bcf-5201-4fbe-93ea-085bea462084.text:
Oh, hello again! How was I... do you think I was
convincing?

abad6441-e13f-46ab-a3f0-b002eea6afed.title: Phillipa
abad6441-e13f-46ab-a3f0-b002eea6afed.text:
Ohhh good! I do hope Juliet will be pleased as well! That
dashing young Romeo must be beside himself with
excitement! Have you told him the good news yet?

939354b1-e6a0-45e7-9d74-d5aaa422c656.title: Phillipa
939354b1-e6a0-45e7-9d74-d5aaa422c656.text:
Good, good... you lucky thing, I can't wait to see the
look on his face!

25e14fd5-fce0-4cbf-ba46-317b7aa0ae13.title: Phillipa
25e14fd5-fce0-4cbf-ba46-317b7aa0ae13.text:
Hello, I seem to be getting on really well with that
dashing lovely dovely, Romeo... Pity about poor Juliet...
she missed out there I reckon!
